This paper deals with decision making under uncertainty, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of influence diagrams and junction trees is also related to probabilistic graphical models (cs.DM) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, game theory (cs.GT) may also be relevant due to the focus on optimal decision policies.
